classDiagram
    %% PawPal+ initial design. Update as the implementation evolves.

    class Pet {
        +str name
        +str species
        +str breed
        +int age_years
        +str notes
        +update_info(**fields) None
    }

    class Owner {
        +str name
        +list~Pet~ pets
        +int daily_minutes_available
        +dict preferences
        +add_pet(pet) None
        +update_info(**fields) None
    }

    class Task {
        +str id
        +Pet pet
        +str title
        +int duration_minutes
        +str priority
        +str category
        +str notes
        +update(**fields) None
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +Owner owner
        +list~Task~ tasks
        +sort_tasks() list~Task~
        +build_plan() Plan
        +explain_choice(task) str
    }

    class Plan {
        +list scheduled
        +list skipped
        +int total_minutes_used
        +int day_budget
        +render() list
        +explain() str
    }

    Owner "1" --> "*" Pet : has
    Pet "1" --> "*" Task : has
    Scheduler --> Owner : uses
    Scheduler --> Task : uses
    Scheduler --> Plan : produces
